0:18:59.040,0:19:01.220
Just wait for God's time and it would be the best.

0:19:01.220,0:19:07.460
If you are a tailor or whatever profession you are, just be satisfied with what you have.

0:19:07.460,0:19:10.460
Ask God to help you.

0:19:10.460,0:19:11.600
Thank you.

0:19:11.600,0:19:18.520
