We have heard from the brothers, who have been able to share with us their experiences

0:19:27.760,0:19:32.080
from their journey to Libya.

0:19:32.080,0:19:34.460
They are not the first set of deportees.

0:19:34.460,0:19:43.200
For months, we have been receiving thousands and thousands of deportees from Libya.

0:19:43.200,0:19:57.520
As they said, after their landing here they made the decision to come to The SCOAN, having heard of

0:19:57.520,0:20:02.500
the goodness of the God Almighty through His anointed, Prophet T.B. Joshua and Emmanuel TV partners

0:20:02.500,0:20:06.060
in the lives of other deportees.

0:20:06.060,0:20:11.220
They said that was why they also made this decision to come down to The SCOAN.

0:20:11.220,0:20:13.920
They are here today sharing their experience.

0:20:13.920,0:20:31.220
When they and thousands of other deportees came to The SCOAN, they were welcomed and given money.

0:20:31.220,0:20:42.500
They have come here to share the experience to the world and give advice that

0:20:42.500,0:20:48.140
if you want embark on any journey abroad, it must be taken legally.

0:20:48.140,0:20:49.720
We have heard their experience.

0:20:49.720,0:20:56.620
They have made their heart desires known to Prophet of God - T.B. Joshua.

0:20:56.620,0:21:03.100
They are here today to receive help from man of God -T.B. Joshua and Emmanuel TV partners,

0:21:03.100,0:21:10.720
so that they can be useful to the society and avoid falling into bad companion.

0:21:10.720,0:21:15.280
They have shared their experiences during the Sunday service.

0:21:15.280,0:21:19.140
The man of God has made us understand that we are called to respond to all humans in need -

0:21:19.140,0:21:21.240
that is what love entails.

0:21:21.240,0:21:25.640
We cannot look the other way when our brothers and sisters are in need.

0:21:25.640,0:21:32.220
